  "texts": [
    "The women approached Jonah, their eyes filled with gratitude.",
    "\"Thank you, prophet,\" they said.",
    "\"Thank you for coming to our city and warning us of our sins.",
    "Thank you for helping us to repent and turn our hearts to God.\"",
    "Jonah looked at the women, his heart heavy."
  ],
